it.polimi.constraintcomputation.subpropertyidentifier

Class SubPropertyIdentifier

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.action.CHIAAction<SubProperty>
      • it.polimi.constraintcomputation.subpropertyidentifier.SubPropertyIdentifier

  • public class SubPropertyIdentifier
extends CHIAAction<SubProperty>
    This class identifies the sub-automata of the automaton that refer to the black box states of the original model. In particular it isolates the portions of the state space that refer to the black box states of the model into components.
    Each component includes the refinements of the black box states that make the intersection not empty
    Author:
    claudiomenghi

      • SubPropertyIdentifier

        public SubPropertyIdentifier(Checker checker,
                     State blackBoxState)
        creates an identifier that is used to isolate the sub-property that refers to the blackBoxState
        Parameters:
        checker - is the checker that has been used to check the model and the claim
        blackBoxState - is the black box state of interest
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if the checker is null or the blackBoxState is null
        IllegalArgumentException - the blackBoxState must be a black box state of the model
        IllegalStateException - the checking activity must be performed before the sub-property identification
